Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:43.60,Sai,,0,0,0,,A hundred forty years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:47.35,Sai,,0,0,0,,Torajirou lent his body to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:52.46,Sai,,0,0,0,,If Torajirou existed for my sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:57.34,Sai,,0,0,0,,then I existed for Hikaru's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:01:59.77,Sai,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.52,0:02:04.19,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru exists for someone else as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.11,0:02:07.61,Sai,,0,0,0,,And that someone will, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.78,0:02:10.40,Sai,,0,0,0,,be there for another person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:14.61,Sai,,0,0,0,,A millennium becomes two,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:18.04,Sai,,0,0,0,,built up slowly person by person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:25.21,Sai,,0,0,0,,The long path leading to the divine move...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.80,0:02:34.38,Sai,,0,0,0,,My part in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:36.01,Sai,,0,0,0,,is over...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:42.14,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(332,115)}The Sixty-First Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:42.14,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fs56\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy50\fscx330\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}Sai is gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're playing because you wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you're pissing me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine then! I'm going to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Cut it out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:44.95,Background,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You just got back, why are you acting so strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I leave it at the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it can't be, we were playing Go until just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The window was open...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe he got carried off by the wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where... the Go institute maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he went somewhere fun after\Ngetting carried off by the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's never happened before in the\Ntwo years we've been together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:05:01.11,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fad(292,292)}Yuugen (Room of Deep Contemplation) - Check out\Nthe background information shown in the ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:05.91,Background,,0,0,0,,Sai!
