Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:12.83,Thinking,,0,0,0,,So he's not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:15.67,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Where the hell did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Why did you disappear all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:26.43,Background,,0,0,0,,What is it Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:29.31,Background,,0,0,0,,Going into the shed all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:30.48,Background,,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget something here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:52.42,Thinking,,0,0,0,,The stain... it's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:57.55,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Why!? What's going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:00.46,Thinking,,0,0,0,,We were playing Go together, in my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:03.93,Thinking,,0,0,0,,That was it... we do that all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:10.73,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah... the stain had faded a little\Nthe last time we were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:15.06,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He said back then that he was going to disappear soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:18.69,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What did he mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:22.32,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He couldn't... he couldn't have... really disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:24.74,Thinking,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:27.81,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't disappear without saying a word to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:31.12,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai and I were always together!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, what are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.34,0:06:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A ghost's going to haunt you\Nif you stay in there too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I want one to haunt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think makes ghosts disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you talking about\Nmaking peace with their life?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when they've accomplished\Neverything they want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:57.69,Background,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Going home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:08.45,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He hasn't mastered the divine move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:12.08,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He would still want to stay in this world\Nfor millennium after millennium.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:15.58,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It has to be my room! He has to be\Nhiding somewhere in my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:17.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He was in my room just this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.38,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:37.34,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He just went somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:08:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's never happened before, but he must have\Nfigured out how to go off on his own!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:06.55,Background,,0,0,0,,He was in a bad mood lately, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:11.30,Background,,0,0,0,,He probably flew off somewhere\Nfor a change of pace...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he... know how to fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have learned how to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He just went somewhere for fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:33.99,Background,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you? Why did you go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You came all the way, you should\Nhave played a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of places do ghosts like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:49.51,Background,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to know!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Like his own grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Or places he has fond memories of?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:05.11,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have a grave... does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:07.57,Thinking,,0,0,0,,A place he has fond memories of...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thanks a lot, I think I figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.28,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hey! Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:16.49,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He wasn't in the shed where we first met...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:20.62,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I guess it's not somewhere he has memories with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Torajirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai said that he met Torajirou on Innoshima...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.55,0:09:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Innoshima... Innoshima...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroshima!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's frickin' far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:42.23,Background,,0,0,0,,Here it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:47.98,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He... complained constantly about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:51.45,Thinking,,0,0,0,,but he liked Torajirou...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:55.32,Background,,0,0,0,,Man, so what!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:57.79,Background,,0,0,0,,I spent time together with Sai, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.11,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll find you no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:07.21,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I won't let you just disappear all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.38,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I won't, you hear me Sai!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:20.06,Background,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Innoshima...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I make it back today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I may find some leads,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,as to where Sai went.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Want a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.87,0:10:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.42,Background,,0,0,0,,Tokyo station?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:46.71,Background,,0,0,0,,You're taking a trip somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And, isn't Innoshima where Honinbou\NShuusaku was born?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:56.01,Background,,0,0,0,,That would be fun... I wish I could go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:59.64,Background,,0,0,0,,I was really busy during Golden week this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:11:05.02,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fad(292,292)}Translator's note: In early May, the Japanese have 3 national holidays in a row,\Nfollowed by a weekend. So this gives them 5 holidays in a row, making it the\Nlongest break from work they have in the year. This week is called 'Golden Week'.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna drop this car off at the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, Mount Fuji looks beautiful today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawai-san could you keep your voice down?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! You have to make the\Nmost out of vacation trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're just tagging along...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to get on a bus to Innoshima from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That bus! It says it's to Innoshima!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:46.85,Background,,0,0,0,,It's that bus! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Man... why do kids always have to run?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.28,Background,,0,0,0,,We're crossing the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.54,Background,,0,0,0,,Of course! It's the ISLAND Innoshima, ISLAND.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:08.96,Background,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, it's not supposed\Nto be that long of a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:14.59,Background,,0,0,0,,It says the Shuusaku Memorial Museum is a 15\N minute walk away after we get off the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:17.01,Background,,0,0,0,,Shuusaku Memorial Museum?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.01,0:12:24.01,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HF8F1EB&\an7\bord0\blur0\shad0\pos(0,0)}{\p1}m 215 72 l 451 72 451 103 215 104{\p0}
