Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:49.75,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Stop hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.46,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he isn't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:05.51,Background,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing over there? It's this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you praying or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.36,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:31.50,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's not here after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:35.50,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh! Wow! They have Go boards, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this... a Go board Torajirou used to play on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Torajirou?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Master Shuusaku's childhood name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is the board he used when\Nhe played with his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:52.14,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:53.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:55.86,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.03,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Shuusaku's grave is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hey! You! Quit running already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh... this is why I hate kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, he's a pro player who\Njust became first dan this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:27.14,Background,,0,0,0,,And he said he wanted to go to where Master\NShuusaku was born, so here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:30.06,Background,,0,0,0,,I brought him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:31.98,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:37.36,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Master Shuusaku would\Nbe happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:34.85,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:37.40,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai?
Comment: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:51.66,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,&H564855& &H2E2C30& and &H403E43& and 256 -74
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:51.66,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs21\blur1\1c&H403E43&\4c&HFFFFFF&\fscx100\fscy101\bord0\shad1.5\frz356.5\move(403,256,403,-74)}G\N{\fscy100)}R\N{\fscy99)}A\N{\fscy98)}V\N{\fscy97)}E\N\N\N{\fscy90)}O\N{\fscy90)}F\N\N\N{\fscy84)}S\N{\fscy81)}H\N{\fscy81)}U\N{\fscy81)}U\N{\fscy77)}S\N{\fscy77)}A\N{\fscy75)}K\N{\fscy74)}U
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:45.53,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:11.10,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\blur1\1c&H564855&\4c&HFFFFFF&\fscx95\fscy78.3\bord0\shad1.5\move(423,-16,423,-135)}S\N\NH\N\NU\N\NU\N\NS\N\NA\N\NK\N\NU\N\N'
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:12.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:16.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Where did you go...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:21.12,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I... have no idea what's going on anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:35.46,Thinking,,0,0,0,,There's no use in getting dejected...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:37.58,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I've got to look for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:56.98,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I guess he's not here after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:16:00.48,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:06.90,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I came all this way looking for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:10.82,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sai! Please! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:12.66,Thinking,,0,0,0,,You can hear me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:19.21,Background,,0,0,0,,You sure took a long time visiting the graves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.21,0:16:22.71,Background,,0,0,0,,I had no idea you looked up to Shuusaku so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:23.96,Background,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:25.76,Background,,0,0,0,,Don't deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:29.30,Background,,0,0,0,,I've already decided on where to go next for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:30.14,Background,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:32.35,Background,,0,0,0,,Housenji temple in Takehara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:35.18,Background,,0,0,0,,The lady at the Memorial Museum told me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:38.23,Background,,0,0,0,,She said Shuusaku played Go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the Go board they used at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and these are the stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we actually get to see them like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:17:03.04,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He came here with Torajirou a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It is important to preserve them,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think it's also important to let the\Npeople who want to see it, see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! The guys at the Go Salon\Nare going to be so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:23.73,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:26.53,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:29.74,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He isn't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:32.32,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Why, Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:37.20,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Didn't you want to come to where Torajirou was?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home!? You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to and back from Hiroshima to Tokyo\Nin a day!? And this late at night!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home! I told my mom\Nthat I'm only going out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have school tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home alone then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going sight seeing tomorrow, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? There's more!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy at the last site told\Nme about two more places.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I don't have the money to stay overnight...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw man... I'll lend it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.53,Background,,0,0,0,,Wait! I've got to call home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.70,0:18:16.87,Background,,0,0,0,,Hey! The phones over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:33.38,ed64_romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\1c&H625B5E&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\frz358\pos(408,173)}Okonomiyaki
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Eat up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We visited both places this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't not be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.49,0:18:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, take your time eating lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you see the Go salon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:00.99,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\fscy45\1a&HFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H95&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord2\blur1\shad1\pos(322,317)}GO IGO CLUB
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:02.75,Background,,0,0,0,,I'll go play the guys over there for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pay for the bill here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Come pick me up when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:36.74,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He was nowhere to be found, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:39.99,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him today or yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:45.04,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll go back to Tokyo already,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:47.29,Thinking,,0,0,0,,if he's not over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:53.84,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:57.59,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He just might be back in my room when I get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:01.35,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If I see Sai at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:05.60,Thinking,,0,0,0,,then, someday, we'll come back here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:09.48,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'd be ecstatic if I took him around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:13.69,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\fscy45\1a&HFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\3a&H95&\4c&HFFFFFF&\bord2\blur1\shad1\pos(322,317)}GO IGO CLUB
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:18.45,Background,,0,0,0,,I feel bad for Kawai-san, but\NI'll drag him back to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.62,Background,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the crap already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one that suggested it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one that lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:36.59,Background,,0,0,0,,Kawai-san...
