Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.09,0:22:15.34,Background,,0,0,0,,I, Umezawa Yukari,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.41,0:22:16.86,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(667,0)\fs22.5\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H127AF4&\4c&H127AF4&\bord1.5\shad0.5\pos(346,345)}Teacher Yukari
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.34,0:22:19.73,Background,,0,0,0,,once took you through the land of Honinbou\NShuusaku's birth, Innoshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:21.95,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(501,501)\fs22.5\bord1.5\3c&H009000&\4c&H009000&\shad0.5\pos(322,332)}Memorial Monument for Honinbou Shuusaku
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.25,0:22:26.92,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(501,501)\fs27.5\bord1.5\fscy95\3c&H009000&\4c&H009000&\shad0.5\pos(322,332)}Shuusaku Memorial Museum
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.02,0:22:28.02,Background,,0,0,0,,So this time, we'll take you through the\Nother grave of Honinbou Shuusaku,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:30.29,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(501,501)\fs28\bord1.5\fscy95\3c&H009000&\4c&H009000&\shad0.5\pos(227,332)}Grave of Shuusaku
