Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.02,0:22:30.47,Background,,0,0,0,,Honmyouji temple in Sugamo of Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you around!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.69,0:22:30.88,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,0)\fs25\3c&HF627EF&\4c&HF627EF&\bord1.5\shad0.5\move(475,397,400,342)}Mai
